                    <span>I recently finished your book "Deal Terms" and found it extremely<BR>helpful as we are looking into our first round of financing.<P>This book showed me numerous issues that I would have definitely overlooked or simply not thought of.<BR>Â <BR>Thanks for writing Deal Terms. Definitely an invaluable<BR>reference for anyone in business!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Direct to the Deal Terms</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
